title: SmartInvoice Grant Proposal
description: Smart Invoice builds trust between payer and payee by creating a secure neutral channel for transferring money. The payer proves their commitment by locking money in the contract, and controls when it is released to the payee. No middle party, no leap of faith, and you don’t even have to use the word escrow if you don’t want to.

title: Black Sky Nexus
description: We are a small collective of writers, researchers, artists, and technologists who are launching Black Sky Nexus, an open source wiki and zine. This Moloch grant request is to fund 3 research reports and 3 articles / guides which would be included in Black Sky Nexus. The topics will be related to privacy on Ethereum, network decentralization, the landscape of zero-knowledge development, and more.

title: Mycelium Research - Educational Resources
description: This funding will help support one dedicated full time researcher to create in-depth educational resources for the ecosystem.
